HEADWORD: iron maiden
<hw>i"ron maid"en</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An instrument of
torture used in the middle ages, consisting of a box large enough to
hold a person, often in the shape of a woman, and having multiple sharp
spikes on the inside. Called also the <altname>iron maiden of
Nuremberg</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ironmaster</ent>⟦br⟧
